ださい。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"l-information-modal__btn\">\n      <a class=\"m-btn -confirm-button\" href=\"javascript:void(0)\">確認しました</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<!--l-information-modal-->\n\n<div class=\"l-floating-contact\">\n  <a class=\"m-btn -contact\" href=\"/business-contact/\">\n    <img src=\"/assets/img/ico-contact-white.svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"18\" alt=\"企業お問合せアイコン\">\n    <span>企業ご担当者様<br>お問合せ</span>\n  </a>\n</div>\n<!--l-floating-contact-->\n\n<div class=\"l-wrapper\">\n\n  <main class=\"l-main\">\n\n    <div class=\"p-mv -service -new-graduate\">\n      <div class=\"p-mv__inner m-inner\">\n        <h1 class=\"p-mv__ttl\">新卒採用支援</h1>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <!--.p-mv-->\n\n    <section class=\"service-feature p-sec -no-space js-inview anime-up\">\n      <div class=\"m-inner -size-l\">\n        <h2 class=\"service-feature__read\">インターンシップから選考期まで、<br class=\"sp-only\">カスタマイズにも対応。<br>採用課題に応じた<br class=\"sp-only\">効率的なサポートを提供します。</h2>\n        <div class=\"p-sec__body\">\n          <p class=\"service-feature__ttl\">feature</p>\n          <ul class=\"service-feature__lists -col-5\">\n            <li class=\"service-feature__list\">\n              <img src=\"/assets/img/service/ico-feature-group.svg\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" alt=\"鈴与グループのネットワークを活かし、幅広い学生にアプローチ\" loading=\"lazy\">\n              <h3 class=\"service-feature__list-ttl\">鈴与グループの<br>ネットワークを活かし、<br>幅広い学生にアプローチ</h3>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"service-feature__list\">\n              <img src=\"/assets/img/service/ico-feature-event.svg\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" alt=\"効果的なイベント企画で、企業の魅力を最大限に発信\" loading=\"lazy\">\n              <h3 class=\"service-feature__list-ttl\">効果的なイベント<br class=\"sp-only\">企画で、<br class=\"pc-only\">企業の魅力を<br class=\"sp-only\">最大限に発信</h3>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"service-feature__list\">\n              <img src=\"/assets/img/service/ico-feature-matching.svg\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" alt=\"人材紹介ノウハウを活かし、学生と企業の理想的なマッチングを実現\" loading=\"lazy\">\n              <h3 class=\"service-feature__list-ttl\">人材紹介ノウハウを<br class=\"sp-only\">活かし、<br class=\"pc-only\">学生と企業の<br class=\"sp-only\">理想的な<br class=\"pc-only\">マッチングを<br class=\"sp-only\">実現</h3>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"service-feature__list\">\n              <img src=\"/assets/img/service/ico-feature-recruit.svg\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" alt=\"企画から運営フォローまで採用活動をトータル支援\" loading=\"lazy\">\n              <h3 class=\"service-feature__list-ttl\">企画から<br class=\"sp-only\">運営フォローまで<br>採用活動をトータル支援</h3>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"service-feature__list\">\n              <img src=\"/assets/img/service/ico-feature-privacy.jpg\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" alt=\"安心のプライバシーマーク取得\" loading=\"lazy\">\n              <h3 class=\"service-feature__list-ttl\">安心の<br>プライバシーマーク取得</h3>\n            </li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n    <!--.feature-->\n\n    <section class=\"service-cases p-sec js-inview anime-up\">\n      <div class=\"service-cases__inner m-inner -sp-none\">\n        <h2 class=\"m-ttl\" data-en=\"support\">\n          <span class=\"m-ttl__main\">支援内容</span>\n        </h2>\n        <div class=\"p-sec__body\">\n          <h3 class=\"m-ttl-2 m-tc\">新卒・第二新卒人材紹介</h3>\n          <p class=\"p-sec__body-txt m-block-space-s\">人材紹介ビジネスで培った豊富なノウハウを活かし、貴社の採用ニーズに応じた最適な人材を選定・ご提案。</p>\n          <div class=\"service-cases__slide splide\" id=\"js-slide-training-01\">\n            <div class=\"splide__track\">\n              <ul class=\"service-cases__cards splide__list\">\n                <li class=\"service-cases__card -type02 splide__slide\">\n                  <input class=\"service-cases__card-more\" id=\"case1\" type=\"checkbox\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                  <div class=\"service-cases__card-front\">\n                      <div class=\"service-cases__card-inner\">\n                        <p class=\"service-cases__card-txt\">ミスマッチの少ない<br>出会いを実現</p>\n                        <label class=\"service-cases__card-button\" for=\"case1\" aria-hidden=\"true\">内容を見る</label>\n                      </div>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"service-cases__card-back\">\n                      <div class=\"service-cases__card-inner\">\n                        <p class=\"service-cases__card-txt\"></p>\n                        <p class=\"service-cases__card-txt\">専任アドバイザーが学生一人ひとりに対応し、貴社の魅力を的確に伝達。志望度を醸成することで、企業理解を深めた学生との最適なマッチングを実現します。</p>\n                        <label class=\"service-cases__card-button\" for=\"case1\" aria-hidden=\"true\">戻る</label>\n                      </div>\n                  </div>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"service-cases__card -type02 splide__slide\">\n                  <input class=\"service-cases__card-more\" id=\"case2\" type=\"checkbox\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                  <div class=\"service-cases__card-front\">\n                      <div class=\"service-cases__card-inner\">\n                        <p class=\"service-cases__card-txt\">採用活動の効率化と<br>負担軽減</p>\n                        <label class=\"service-cases__card-button\" for=\"case2\" aria-hidden=\"true\">内容を見る</label>\n                      </div>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"service-cases__card-back\">\n                      <div class=\"service-cases__card-inner\">\n                        <p class=\"service-cases__card-txt\"></p>\n                        <p class=\"service-cases__card-txt\">企業のニーズに基づきターゲット学生を集め、スクリーニング後に最適な候補者をご提案。採用活動の負担を軽減し、効率的な採用支援をサポートします。</p>\n                        <label class=\"service-cases__card-button\" for=\"case2\" aria-hidden=\"true\">戻る</label>\n                      </div>\n                  </div>\n                </li>\n              </ul>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"splide__arrows sp-only\">\n              <button class=\"splide__arrow splide__arrow--prev\"></button>\n              <button class=\"splide__arrow splide__arrow--next\"></button>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"p-sec__body\">\n          <h3 class=\"m-ttl-2 m-tc\">採用支援</h3>\n          <p class=\"p-sec__body-txt m-block-space-s\">鈴与グループ採用支援のノウハウを最大限生かし、母集団形成から認知拡大、選考まで幅広くサポート。</p>\n          <div class=\"service-cases__slide splide\" id=\"js-slide-training-02\">\n            <div class=\"splide__track\">\n              <ul class=\"service-cases__cards splide__list\">\n                <li class=\"service-cases__card -line-2 -type02 splide__slide\">\n                  <input class=\"service-cases__card-more\" id=\"support1-case1\" type=\"checkbox\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                  <div class=\"service-cases__card-front\">\n                      <div class=\"service-cases__card-inner\">\n                        <p class=\"service-cases__card-txt\">イベントの<br class=\"sp-only\">企画・運営</p>\n                        <label class=\"service-cases__card-button\" for=\"support1-case1\" aria-hidden=\"true\">内容を見る</label>\n                      </div>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"service-cases__card-back\">\n                      <div class=\"service-cases__card-inner\">\n                        <p class=\"service-cases__card-txt\"></p>\n                        <p class=\"service-cases__card-txt\">企業の採用ニーズに合わせ、業種・職種別のイベントや説明会、座談会など多様な形式のイベントを開催。時期に応じた最適なコンテンツを提供し、質の高い候補者との出会いを促進します。</p>\n                        <label class=\"service-cases__card-button\" for=\"support1-case1\" aria-hidden=\"true\">戻る</label>\n                      </div>\n                  </div>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"service-cases__card -line-2 -type02 splide__slide\">\n                  <input class=\"service-cases__card-more\" id=\"support1-case2\" type=\"checkbox\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                  <div class=\"service-cases__card-front\">\n                      <div class=\"service-cases__card-inner\">\n                        <p class=\"service-cases__card-txt\">就活メディアを<br>活用した情報発信</p>\n                        <label class=\"service-cases__card-button\" for=\"support1-case2\" aria-hidden=\"true\">内容を見る</label>\n                      </div>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"service-cases__card-back\">\n                      <div class=\"service-cases__card-inner\">\n                        <p class=\"service-cases__card-txt\"></p>\n                        <p class=\"service-cases__card-txt\">就職活動支援サイトやSNSを活用した情報発信で、様々な角度から企業の魅力を紹介します。認知度に依存せず、ターゲット層に特徴や文化を効果的に伝えます。</p>\n                        <label class=\"service-cases__card-button\" for=\"support1-case2\" aria-hidden=\"true\">戻る</label>\n                      </div>\n                  </div>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"service-cases__card -line-2 -type02 splide__slide\">\n                  <input class=\"service-cases__card-more\" id=\"support1-case3\" type=\"checkbox\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                  <div class=\"service-cases__card-front\">\n                      <div class=\"service-cases__card-inner\">\n                        <p class=\"service-cases__card-txt\">採用力強化サポート</p>\n                        <label class=\"service-cases__card-button\" for=\"support1-case3\" aria-hidden=\"true\">内容を見る</label>\n                      </div>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"service-cases__card-back\">\n                      <div class=\"service-cases__card-inner\">\n                        <p class=\"service-cases__card-txt\"></p>\n                        <p class=\"service-cases__card-txt\">定期的に情報交換会やセミナーを開催し、採用マーケットに関する最新情報や企業の成功事例など、採用担当者にとって有益な情報を提供します。</p>\n                        <label class=\"service-cases__card-button\" for=\"support1-case3\" aria-hidden=\"true\">戻る</label>\n                      </div>\n                  </div>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"service-cases__card -line-2 -type02 splide__slide\">\n                  <input class=\"service-cases__card-more\" id=\"support1-case4\" type=\"checkbox\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                  <div class=\"service-cases__card-front\">\n                      <div class=\"service-cases__card-inner\">\n                        <p class=\"service-cases__card-txt\">教育機関との<br class=\"sp-only\">関係強化</p>\n                        <label class=\"service-cases__card-button\" for=\"support1-case4\" aria-hidden=\"true\">内容を見る</label>\n                      </div>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"service-cases__card-back\">\n                      <div class=\"service-cases__card-inner\">\n                        <p class=\"service-cases__card-txt\"></p>\n                        <p class=\"service-cases__card-txt\">定期的に大学を訪問し、企業情報やイベント情報を共有しています。学校との関係を深めることで、優れた人材の確保につなげます。</p>\n                        <label class=\"service-cases__card-button\" for=\"support1-case4\" aria-hidden=\"true\">戻る</label>\n                      </div>\n                  </div>\n                </li>\n              </ul>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"splide__arrows sp-only\">\n              <button class=\"splide__arrow splide__arrow--prev\"></button>\n              <button class=\"splide__arrow splide__arrow--next\"></button>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n    <!--.cases-->\n\n    <section class=\"service-result service-bg-left p-sec js-inview anime-up\">\n      <div class=\"m-inner -sp-none\">\n        <h2 class=\"m-ttl\" data-en=\"result\">\n          <span class=\"m-ttl__main\">対応実績</span>\n        </h2>\n\n        <section class=\"p-sec__body\">\n          <h3 class=\"m-ttl-2 m-tc\">新卒学生向けイベント</h3>\n          <ul class=\"service-result__lists -event\">\n            <li class=\"p-sec__body\">\n\n              <div class=\"p-sec__body-inner\">\n                <h4 class=\"m-ttl-3\">インターンシップイベント</h4>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"service-result__slide m-block-space-m splide\" id=\"js-slide-result-01\">\n                <div class=\"splide__track\">\n                  <ul class=\"service-result__cards splide__list\">\n                    <li class=\"service-result__card splide__slide\">\n                      <img src=\"/assets/img/service/new-graduate/ico-result-festa.svg\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" alt=\"就活フェスタ\" loading=\"lazy\">\n                      <h5 class=\"service-result__card-ttl\">就活フェスタ<br>（鈴与グループ向け）</h5>\n                      <p class=\"service-result__card-txt\">夏の大型対面イベント</p>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"service-result__card splide__slide\">\n                      <img src=\"/assets/img/service/new-graduate/ico-result-shimizu.svg\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" alt=\"SHIMIZU×物流\" loading=\"lazy\">\n                      <h5 class=\"service-result__card-ttl\">SHIMIZU×物流</h5>\n                      <p class=\"service-result__card-txt\">清水地区物流企業合同イベント</p>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"service-result__card splide__slide\">\n                      <img src=\"/assets/img/service/new-graduate/ico-result-web.svg\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" alt=\"webチャンネル\" loading=\"lazy\">\n                      <h5 class=\"service-result__card-ttl\">webチャンネル</h5>\n                      <p class=\"service-result__card-txt\">90分程度の業界研究チャンネル</p>\n                    </li>\n                  </ul>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"splide__arrows sp-only\">\n                  <button class=\"splide__arrow splide__arrow--prev\"></button>\n                  <button class=\"splide__arrow splide__arrow--next\"></button>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"p-sec__body\">\n              <div class=\"p-sec__body-inner\">\n                <h3 class=\"m-ttl-3\">選考イベント</h3>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"service-result__slide m-block-space-m splide\" id=\"js-slide-result-02\">\n                <div class=\"splide__track\">\n                  <ul class=\"service-result__cards splide__list\">\n                    <li class=\"service-result__card splide__slide\">\n                      <img src=\"/assets/img/service/new-graduate/ico-result-competition.svg\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" alt=\"説明選考会\" loading=\"lazy\">\n                      <h5 class=\"service-result__card-ttl\">説明選考会</h5>\n                      <p class=\"service-result__card-txt\">選考要素を織り交ぜた複数社合同選考会</p>\n                    </li>\n                  </ul>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"splide__arrows sp-only\">\n                  <button class=\"splide__arrow splide__arrow--prev\"></button>\n                  <button class=\"splide__arrow splide__arrow--next\"></button>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </li>\n          </ul>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"p-sec__body\">\n          <h3 class=\"m-ttl-2 m-tc\">新卒採用活動サポート</h3>\n          <ul class=\"service-result__lists -support\">\n            <li class=\"p-sec__body\">\n            <div class=\"p-sec__body-inner\">\n                <h4 class=\"m-ttl-3\">企業向けMTG</h4>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"service-result__slide m-block-space-m splide\" id=\"js-slide-result-03\">\n                <div class=\"splide__track\">\n                  <ul class=\"service-result__cards splide__list\">\n                    <li class=\"service-result__card splide__slide\">\n                      <img src=\"/assets/img/service/new-graduate/ico-result-kickoff.svg\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" alt=\"新卒採用キックオフミーティング\" loading=\"lazy\">\n                      <h5 class=\"service-result__card-ttl\">新卒採用キックオフ<br>ミーティング</h5>\n                      <p class=\"service-result__card-txt\">新卒採用活動のスタートを切るための戦略共有イベント</p>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"service-result__card splide__slide\">\n                      <img src=\"/assets/img/service/new-graduate/ico-res